00:10:46.040 --> 00:10:53.190 position:56%
Well, Bohdan Hilash has a collection
of so many instruments, you know,

00:10:53.190 --> 00:10:55.410
so many flutes and you know,

00:10:55.410 --> 00:11:00.350
he's also one of the really great
contra base clarinet players

00:11:00.350 --> 00:11:02.500
and contra base saxophone players.

00:11:02.500 --> 00:11:05.060
There aren't too many
of them, and he --

00:11:05.060 --> 00:11:07.880
you know, one of the most wonderful
things about working with Bohdan is

00:11:07.880 --> 00:11:13.120 position:56%
that he has this incredible range of
instruments and instrumental skills,

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:16.210
and so when we're working
on something we try

00:11:16.210 --> 00:11:20.690
to find what the best
